PrecisAmendments to the TEXTILE LABELLING AND ADVERTISING REGULATIONS which specify who is eligible to possess a registered identification number, set out the conditions under which a textile dealer's identification number may be revoked, and make other minor editorial changes.

precis:
Amendments to the TEXTILE LABELLING AND ADVERTISING REGULATIONS which
specify who is eligible to possess a registered identification number,
set out the conditions under which a textile dealer's identification number
may be revoked, and make other minor editorial changes.
